{"tid":739880,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲人去廁所洗手可唔可以斯文啲","createTime":"2018-07-12T12:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:16:11.000Z","uid":115189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f07828b7519e06e5fbae1fe1da5f80ecdb8b45d1","tid":739880,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"今日同男朋友行商場，行到咁上下佢話急屎，咁啱我又想去洗個臉，就去咗廁所啦<br />\n<br />\n洗洗下臉，隔離嗰個洗手洗到龍飛鳳舞咁<br />\n<br />\n啲水彈曬落我隻玉手度，都唔知有幾多細菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就話佢兩句咁啦，點知佢就起曬鋼，話咩少少事，咪自己洗翻乾靜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我夠識洗啦，我係話佢動力好大，好冇禮貌<br />\n<br />\n點知佢仲繼續喺洗手盤度細細聲咁講嘢，單單打打，真係勁嬲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩今次男朋友喺廁格度聽到我把聲，出嚟兇佢走<br />\n<br />\n其實大家洗手可唔可以斯文少少呢，做多一步，尊重下人好難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f975fcea34eeb4e4ab9dd041eaf649a3e43fd646","tid":739880,"uid":64343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"GAY"},{"pid":"f024e54f7c4006b9ab31bf66519175ab1cf9fe25","tid":739880,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"死gay佬洗手都咁多嗲就入女廁啦"},{"pid":"f2a988ddc14922373a6d76528728af941dfd8090","tid":739880,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f024e54f7c4006b9ab31bf66519175ab1cf9fe25","tid":739880,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"死gay佬洗手都咁多嗲就入女廁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"尊重，ok?"},{"pid":"951fed15d7a7ec0f2b2d6266e1249516b4e7ace5","tid":739880,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">This</span></strong></span>"},{"pid